on my fan at the festival,

134
00:15:31,388 --> 00:15:33,474
but he has not brought it up since.

135
00:15:33,557 --> 00:15:36,393
If a man confuses you,
he does not like you.

136
00:15:36,477 --> 00:15:38,145
If you want to know how he feels,

137
00:15:38,228 --> 00:15:40,272
go up to him first.

138
00:15:40,356 --> 00:15:42,650
