Do not worry about your future.

163
00:17:14,366 --> 00:17:17,244
Soon, I will marry a handsome man.

164
00:17:18,454 --> 00:17:21,874
I will meet the man destined for me.

165
00:17:34,928 --> 00:17:37,848
