how much you want to brag,

166
00:17:37,931 --> 00:17:41,351
remind yourself that others might
have something you do not,

167
00:17:41,435 --> 00:17:43,270
and keep it to yourself.

168
00:17:45,105 --> 00:17:47,274
When I do meet the one,

169
00:17:48,275 --> 00:17:50,986
I will give him a pillow
I embroidered myself

170
00:17:52,321 --> 00:17:54,615
so that we can meet in our dreams as well.

171
